dct_title_s: Automobile road map touring Santa Barbara and vicinity
dct_alternative_sm: Automobile road map touring Santa Barbara and vicinity Showing boulevards and highways, beach and mountain resorts
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; A.J.W.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, resorts, lighthouse, oil wells, mission.
Belongs to a series of maps showing roads in California.
